<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN"
	 "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
	  xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal">
	<head>
		<meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
		<title>Welcome To NextThought</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<p>Hi <span tal:content="options/profile/realname" class="realname">John Doe</span>!</p>.

		<p>
			Thank you for creating your new account, and welcome to
			NextThought!
		</p>

		<p>
			Your username is <span tal:content="options/user/username" class="username">username</span>.
			Please go to <a href="http://nextthought.com" tal:attributes="href request/application_url" tal:content="request/application_url">http://nextthought.com</a>
			to log into your account.
		</p>
		<p>
			With NextThought, you can easily collaborate with your classmates and
			personalize your content through notes, highlights, and whiteboards.
			Explore the NextThought Help Center in your Library to get started and
			learn more about the exciting interactive features NextThought has to
			offer.
		</p>

		<p>
		Sincerely,<br />
		NextThought
		</p>

		<p>
		If you feel this email was sent in error, or this account was created
		without your consent, you may email us at <a href="mailto:support@nextthought.com">support@nextthought.com</a>.
		</p>

	</body>
</html>
